(44, 10, 18, 44, 11, 11, 11, 'Simon, which was surnamed Peter', 'Connection of Peter''s Encounter', 'Both passages emphasize the arrival of men sent to Peter. The mention of ''three men'' in Acts 11:11 connects directly to the context of Peter being sought in Acts 10:18.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 10, 19, 44, 8, 29, 29, 'the Spirit said unto', 'Divine Guidance in Acts', 'Both passages emphasize the role of the Spirit in directing the actions of the apostles. In each instance, the Spirit instructs Peter and Philip to engage with others, highlighting the theme of divine guidance in their missions.', 'theme', 0.349, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 10, 19, 44, 11, 12, 12, 'the Spirit said unto him', 'Divine Guidance in Peter''s Journey', 'This connection highlights the role of the Spirit in guiding Peter''s actions. In both passages, the Spirit directs Peter to engage with the men seeking him, emphasizing obedience to divine instruction.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 10, 19, 43, 16, 13, 13, 'the Spirit said unto him', 'Guidance of the Spirit', 'This connection highlights the role of the Spirit in guiding believers. In Acts, the Spirit directs Peter to those seeking him, while in John, the Spirit is described as guiding into all truth.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 10, 19, 46, 12, 11, 11, 'the Spirit said unto him', 'Connection of the Spirit''s Guidance', 'This connection highlights the role of the Spirit in guiding individuals. In Acts, the Spirit directs Peter to those seeking him, while in 1 Corinthians, the Spirit distributes gifts as desired.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 10, 19, 54, 4, 1, 1, 'the Spirit said unto him', 'Connection of Spiritual Guidance', 'This connection highlights the role of the Spirit in guiding believers. In Acts, the Spirit directs Peter to those seeking him, while in 1 Timothy, the Spirit warns of those who will depart from faith, indicating the importance of discernment in spiritual matters.', 'theme', 0.321, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
